name: ~Linkle Cottage Dress~ (Linkle 3.0 Collection)
desc:
Lynx is back in town, and with a new outfit! 

This mod is part of the Linkle 3.0 Collection series. A series of mods that will be official post-release standalone outfits by the Linkle Project team!

This mod adds the Villager's Attire set! 

The standalone Lynx Mod is not required for this mod to work!
Talk to Lynx at Hateno Village's inn to purchase it.
